fileSamples.statement:
(cond : condition) (args : list positive) (vl : list AVal.t) : vl = map (fun r : positive => AE.get r ae) args ->
let (cond', args') :=
  match cond_strength_reduction_match cond args vl with
  | cond_strength_reduction_case1 c _ r2 n1 _ =>
      (Ccompimm (swap_comparison c) n1, r2 :: nil)
  | cond_strength_reduction_case2 c r1 _ _ n2 => (Ccompimm c n2, r1 :: nil)
  | cond_strength_reduction_case3 c _ r2 n1 _ =>
      (Ccompuimm (swap_comparison c) n1, r2 :: nil)
  | cond_strength_reduction_case4 c r1 _ _ n2 => (Ccompuimm c n2, r1 :: nil)
  | cond_strength_reduction_case5 c s a r1 _ _ n2 =>
      (Ccompimm c (eval_static_shift s n2 a), r1 :: nil)
  | cond_strength_reduction_case6 c s a r1 _ _ n2 =>
      (Ccompuimm c (eval_static_shift s n2 a), r1 :: nil)
  | cond_strength_reduction_case7 c _ r2 n1 _ =>
      (Ccomplimm (swap_comparison c) n1, r2 :: nil)
  | cond_strength_reduction_case8 c r1 _ _ n2 => (Ccomplimm c n2, r1 :: nil)
  | cond_strength_reduction_case9 c _ r2 n1 _ =>
      (Ccompluimm (swap_comparison c) n1, r2 :: nil)
  | cond_strength_reduction_case10 c r1 _ _ n2 =>
      (Ccompluimm c n2, r1 :: nil)
  | cond_strength_reduction_case11 c s a r1 _ _ n2 =>
      (Ccomplimm c (eval_static_shiftl s n2 a), r1 :: nil)
  | cond_strength_reduction_case12 c s a r1 _ _ n2 =>
      (Ccompluimm c (eval_static_shiftl s n2 a), r1 :: nil)
  | cond_strength_reduction_case13 c _ r2 n1 _ =>
      if Float.eq_dec n1 Float.zero
      then (Ccompfzero (swap_comparison c), r2 :: nil)
      else (cond, args)
  | cond_strength_reduction_case14 c r1 _ _ n2 =>
      if Float.eq_dec n2 Float.zero
      then (Ccompfzero c, r1 :: nil)
      else (cond, args)
  | cond_strength_reduction_case15 c _ r2 n1 _ =>
      if Float.eq_dec n1 Float.zero
      then (Cnotcompfzero (swap_comparison c), r2 :: nil)
      else (cond, args)
  | cond_strength_reduction_case16 c r1 _ _ n2 =>
      if Float.eq_dec n2 Float.zero
      then (Cnotcompfzero c, r1 :: nil)
      else (cond, args)
  | cond_strength_reduction_case17 c _ r2 n1 _ =>
      if Float32.eq_dec n1 Float32.zero
      then (Ccompfszero (swap_comparison c), r2 :: nil)
      else (cond, args)
  | cond_strength_reduction_case18 c r1 _ _ n2 =>
      if Float32.eq_dec n2 Float32.zero
      then (Ccompfszero c, r1 :: nil)
      else (cond, args)
  | cond_strength_reduction_case19 c _ r2 n1 _ =>
      if Float32.eq_dec n1 Float32.zero
      then (Cnotcompfszero (swap_comparison c), r2 :: nil)
      else (cond, args)
  | cond_strength_reduction_case20 c r1 _ _ n2 =>
      if Float32.eq_dec n2 Float32.zero
      then (Cnotcompfszero c, r1 :: nil)
      else (cond, args)
  | cond_strength_reduction_default cond0 args0 _ => (cond0, args0)
  end in
eval_condition cond' e ## args' m = eval_condition cond e ## args m.

  then (Ointconst Int.zero, nil)
  else

   then (Omove, r :: nil)
   else
    if
     match x with
     | Uns _ m0 => Int.eq (Int.zero_ext m0 (Int.not n)) Int.zero
     | _ => false
     end
    then (Omove, r :: nil)
    else (Oandimm n, r :: nil) in

inv H; auto.
simpl.
replace (Int.and i n) with i; auto.
generalize (Int.eq_spec (Int.zero_ext n0 (Int.not n)) Int.zero); rewrite UNS; intro EQ.

rewrite Int.bits_not by auto.
